cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.HC 

This paper involves the analysis of smartphone application usage data, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI) and data structures and algorithms (cs.SD). The use of deep packet inspection also involves aspects of cybersecurity (cs.CR). The prediction of app usage based on location data also has implications for human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY).
